DOC.brief_summary: This study aims to understand better the effective results from the IMELDA MO22223 P-trial (NCT00929240) and see if the anti-cancer therapies given during its follow-up time after study treatments were terminated possibly had an effect on efficacy results.
DOC.brief_title: Retrospective Data Collection: Post Study Treatment Anticancer Therapy From IMELDA MO22223
DOC.criteria: Having been randomized in the IMELDA MO22223 Ptrial Not having been randomized in the IMELDA MO22223 Ptrial
